Class CreateComputerRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.AmazonWebServiceRequest
      • com.amazonaws.services.directory.model.CreateComputerRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadLimitInfo, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class CreateComputerRequest
extends AmazonWebServiceRequest
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Container for the parameters to the CreateComputer operation.

    Creates a computer account in the specified directory, and joins the computer to the directory.

    See Also:
    AWSDirectoryService.createComputer(CreateComputerRequest), Serialized Form
